cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.GR 

The paper proposes a deep convolutional neural network architecture for image-to-image regression tasks such as relighting, denoising, and colorization. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also emphasizes the end-to-end training of the network without any further machinery, which suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The tasks of relighting, denoising, and colorization involve manipulating image pixels, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) and graphics (cs.GR).
